# A.I.M. - Git Ignore Configuration

# 1. Personal Identity & Secrets
.env
core/CONFIG.json
core/MEMORY.md
core/USER.md
core/IDENTITY.md
core/AGENTS.md
core/TOOLS.md
core/HEARTBEAT.md

# 2. Live Memory & Intelligence
memory/*.md
memory/proposals/*.md
memory/archive/*.md
continuity/*.md
continuity/private/
archive/raw/*.json
archive/index/*.fragments.json
archive/private/
archive/forensic.db
.aim.lock
workstreams/

# 3. Exceptions (Keep Templates)
!core/templates/*.template

# 4. Environment & Tooling
venv/
node_modules/
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.DS_Store
.gemini/
